---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ProjectPageShell from "../components/ProjectPageShell.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Modern Football - Altralight"
    description="Modern Football is our tactical football project: reactive, simulation-first, and built without stale genre baggage."
    bodyClass="project-page"
>
    <ProjectPageShell
        themeClass="project-theme-football"
        eyebrow="Sports Weirdness"
        title="Modern Football"
        intro="A football game built from scratch. Tactical, reactive, and focused on decisions that feel true to the sport."
        status="Core systems are still in active iteration. The simulation keeps improving as we test and learn."
        sideNote="The goal is not just to look like football. The goal is to feel like football decisions actually matter from moment to moment."
        stats={[
            { value: "AI", label: "In active tuning" },
            { value: "Tactics", label: "Core language" },
            { value: "WIP", label: "Taking the time it needs" },
        ]}
        panels={[
            {
                kicker: "Vision",
                title: "Start fresh and stop inheriting bad sports-game habits.",
                body: [
                    "Most football games are polished iterations of older assumptions. Modern Football starts by questioning those assumptions directly.",
                    "That means smarter simulation, cleaner tactical feedback, and gameplay that reacts like a sport with ideas in it, not just a bag of canned animations."
                ]
            },
            {
                kicker: "Philosophy",
                title: "Built different, yes, but for actual reasons.",
                body: [
                    "What if the AI understood shape, risk, and timing better? What if player behavior felt less scripted and more system-driven?",
                    "Those are the questions this project keeps circling while the systems mature."
                ]
            },
            {
                kicker: "Status",
                title: "Still in the lab, one step at a time.",
                body: [
                    "The work right now is in the middle phase: systems development, experimentation, and steady reshaping whenever the simulation reveals a better idea.",
                    "When something is worth showing, it will land here first. Until then, the project gets the time it needs."
                ]
            }
        ]}
        links={[
            { href: "/", label: "Back to Homepage", variant: "secondary" },
            { href: "/blog/", label: "Read progress posts" },
        ]}
    />
</BaseLayout>
